  IntroLines:
  - Text: Vern, something crazy happened to me!
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Dude, you're not gonna believe this...
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: So like, I saw something really weird the other day.
    Tone: 10
    Weight: 1
  DetailLines:
  - Text: It was super strange. Hard to describe really.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I didn't get any proof but I swear it happened.
    Tone: 10
    Weight: 1
  - Text: My friend was there too but he didn't see it.
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  DefenseLines:
  - Text: I'm not making this up, man!
    Tone: 10
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Why would I lie about something like this?
    Tone: 10
    Weight: 1
  - Text: I know what I saw. Probably.
    Tone: 10
    Weight: 1
  AcceptanceLines:
  - Text: Yeah! Exactly!
    Tone: 1
    Weight: 1
  - Text: That's what I was thinking.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Uh, yeah, sure.
    Tone: 8
    Weight: 1
  ExtraDetailLines: []
  ExtraDefenseLines: []
  ConclusionLines:
  - Text: Thanks Vern. You're the best.
    Tone: 0
    Weight: 1
  - Text: Peace out, keep it real.
